WEBVTT

00:00:01.410 --> 00:00:13.914
Well, good evening, family. I'm sorry I'm a little late. We went to church, and as I was sitting in church, the Lord gave me an open-eyed vision about what we're supposed to be praying for tonight.

00:00:13.915 --> 00:00:25.048
So, we're just going to jump right into the river. But I felt led to go over some of the things we saw yesterday when we were praying. Now, we had two videos yesterday.

00:00:25.049 --> 00:00:38.234
Some of you don't know it; the devil interfered with our internet, and so we just kept going and we ended up praying until almost morning, which was amazing.

00:00:38.235 --> 00:00:43.754
The glory of the Lord came in and hit me with Holy Ghost laughter.

00:00:43.755 --> 00:00:50.672
And I'm telling you, I've never done that to that level on a live stream.

00:00:50.673 --> 00:01:01.378
And so it was pretty amazing—the Lord was just bringing refreshing, especially to me and to my son and to my wife, and just blessing us.

00:01:01.379 --> 00:01:07.328
You know, when you are in a place of always pouring out, it's nice to get refreshed.

00:01:07.329 --> 00:01:12.739
And when you get a touch from the Holy Spirit, it's refreshing.

00:01:12.740 --> 00:01:19.015
There's a lot of you that don't know about it. And they say, 'Well, what is that?

00:01:19.016 --> 00:01:25.977
What were you doing?'That's just yielding. You can't make it happen, just like you can't make groaning happen.

00:01:25.978 --> 00:01:37.885
You get over in the flesh and you make things go and act weird, or you can laugh and be in the flesh, but I'd rather be in the flesh in church than in the world, right?

00:01:37.886 --> 00:01:44.879
And so you start out—it's like people say, 'How do you get over there?'You yield.

00:01:44.880 --> 00:01:48.679
You yield to the presence of God. You yield to the anointing.

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:55.615
You yield. 'Holy Spirit, have your way. Have your way. You are the potter; I am the clay.

00:01:55.616 --> 00:02:05.803
I am yielded to you today.'When a pot is on the potter's wheel and it's molding, the pot doesn't say, 'Well, I don't like the way you're pushing.

00:02:05.804 --> 00:02:15.775
I don't like the way you're doing. I want to be this way.'No, it's yielded to the potter. Have your way.

00:02:15.776 --> 00:02:24.639
So, the potter's up there pushing here, and he's putting all the perfections out and doing all the things that he knows to do to make a good pot.

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:32.815
And if you are a yielded vessel, the Holy Spirit will make a good pot. Does that make sense? I'm trying to relate it.

00:02:32.816 --> 00:02:48.071
And so when you're going over into the laughter and you're just yielded, and it starts out with you just laughing and you feel that bubbling up inside of you, the Holy Spirit will do it just like groanings. It's not something that you just fake.

00:02:48.072 --> 00:03:03.151
People go around acting weird and try to roll around in the aisle and mock and try to imitate something, but when it's authentic and you feel the presence of God, it's like Braden said: 'Dad, the tangible presence of the Lord was in our house last night.

00:03:03.153 --> 00:03:11.439
I could feel it.'And you always wonder, because I don't want to be the only one having a good time.

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:15.101
When you're at a party, you want everybody else to be having a good time, too, right?

00:03:15.102 --> 00:03:21.466
You're having a big party, you're celebrating, and Jesus is there, and you're the only one acting crazy.

00:03:21.467 --> 00:03:28.238
I'd say you're the only one in the town getting drunk. You're the town drunk.

00:03:28.239 --> 00:03:34.958
But whenever the Holy Ghost and fire is on you and everybody else is, it's like Acts chapter 2.

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:39.915
It was just the third hour of the day, right? It's just in the middle of the afternoon.

00:03:39.916 --> 00:03:48.238
'Are these men drunk?'They're all thinking they're all wasted, but they weren't.

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:56.819
This is what this is. This is that spoken by the prophet Joel: the day of Pentecost.

00:03:56.820 --> 00:04:02.798
And I truly believe that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:04:02.799 --> 00:04:08.423
And he's still pouring out his spirit on the church just like he did back in Acts chapter 2.

00:04:08.424 --> 00:04:12.990
I truly believe if you are a yielded vessel, we can walk in it.

00:04:12.991 --> 00:04:20.835
And just like Pastor Candace, she was teaching tonight about Moses. He was underneath the old covenant.

00:04:20.836 --> 00:04:43.758
How much more can we walk in the glory and be in the new covenant, the greater glory, and not just be somebody that is every once in a while visiting there, but somebody that lives there, lives in that presence, in that fullness of the glory, that people see it on you in these last days.

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:48.253
So, all right. That's what all that was about. Last night was amazing. I loved it.

00:04:48.254 --> 00:04:54.191
And if you haven't watched that video, I encourage you, if you just want to have a refreshing, to go watch that video.

00:04:54.192 --> 00:05:08.561
As we were praying, the Lord showed me the revival again. And I saw Minneapolis, Minnesota, and I saw a well of revival springing forth out of the dirt.

00:05:08.562 --> 00:05:22.366
It started—do you know how you see cracks in the desert or in a big lake bed whenever the sun has dried up the water and the massive cracks are all in there?

00:05:22.367 --> 00:05:35.020
And you go, 'Wow, this riverbed is really dry and you can touch it.'But if you just dig down a little bit, the water is there.

00:05:35.021 --> 00:05:43.976
You just got to dig down a little bit. Well, the water table is always at a certain level.

00:05:43.977 --> 00:05:57.592
As I was praying into this, I saw the water coming from the fountains from the deep concerning the glory about what we're about to see. And the Lord said, 'Uncap the wells.'Uncap the wells.

00:05:57.593 --> 00:06:07.995
I saw the wells coming uncapped—what was, you know, when you cap a well and it was a springing forth of new water, new fountains of water.

00:06:07.996 --> 00:06:24.760
And all of a sudden, those cracks that were all in Minnesota started to fill up with water, and it was just barely touching the feet, just barely covering the soles of your shoes. And you're getting a little wet.

00:06:24.761 --> 00:06:39.918
But the Lord said, 'I'm going to take it up from where it's just on the soles of your shoes to ankle-deep, to knee-deep, to waist-deep, to over your head.'And he said, 'You can't mess this up.

00:06:39.919 --> 00:06:52.602
You're not big enough to mess this up for what I'm about to do—the harvest of the prayers for the intercessory prayer that has gone forth.

00:06:52.603 --> 00:07:02.619
The seeds of prayer are springing forth.'And the Lord said to us last night, 'Watch this.'And all of a sudden, bam, it was in Minnesota.

00:07:02.620 --> 00:07:09.754
Bam, it went to Tennessee. I saw around Perry Stone's area where he's at, his ministry, springing forth a well.

00:07:09.755 --> 00:07:20.108
And the Lord said, 'Fill my cup, Lord.'I started singing that song, and the more I sang that song, the glory of the Lord started filling me.

00:07:20.109 --> 00:07:37.119
I could feel it. It went from Minnesota to Tennessee, to Mobile, Alabama, to Fort Worth, Texas, to Oklahoma City, to Collinsville, to Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:42.318
Boom, boom, boom. And it went to Nigeria, and it started springing forth wells of revival.

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:50.033
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to pour.'And I saw a wave of revival coming out of Minnesota again.

00:07:50.034 --> 00:07:57.367
I saw a wave of the glory of God coming forth out of it. And the Lord said, 'Pray for Mike Lindell.

00:07:57.368 --> 00:08:06.799
Pray for these people who are running for office in these areas, for Omar to find a new job somewhere else.

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:17.372
Praying for revival. Praying for this major harvest.'And I could see it going, and it was touching down in these cities.

00:08:17.373 --> 00:08:36.754
And he said, 'These are places of harbingers, like harvesters, like crop circles. I don't know how else to say it.

00:08:36.755 --> 00:09:07.322
There are glory zones—better glory zones, glory manifested zones, designated chosen places for the revival that God has put his finger on.'And when I told you I saw the hand of the Lord—five of it—all his fingers went out over the earth and shafts of light shot down from his fingers and made pillars of light coming from his fingers.

00:09:07.323 --> 00:09:31.702
And he said, 'These are the places that I have designated for a major harvest of souls in the last days in Tennessee, in these areas.'And there were shafts of light that shot forth, and there was major revival in America and parts of Australia and Asia and the Middle East, Europe, and Africa.

00:09:31.703 --> 00:09:43.973
And I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, as these shafts of glory came out of the Lord's hand, he said, "I designated these places.

00:09:43.974 --> 00:09:53.449
I saw satanic camps trying to camp themselves around and about these areas to try to prevent the glory from coming.

00:09:53.450 --> 00:10:05.380
But they're no match for our heavenly Father. No matter how big the devil tries to be, even on his best day, he's nothing.

00:10:05.381 --> 00:10:09.963
He's a loser. He's been defeated. And that's what I was trying to tell you all.

00:10:09.964 --> 00:10:17.772
Do you believe that God can make mistakes? Do you believe that you're a mistake?

00:10:17.773 --> 00:10:21.816
That God made a mistake by letting you be here for such a time as this?

00:10:21.817 --> 00:10:27.599
And that was my point in coming across last night when the Lord told me to ask them that.

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:34.908
I don't believe that our heavenly Father can ever make a mistake.

00:10:34.909 --> 00:10:39.678
We are fearfully and wonderfully made, every single one of us.

00:10:39.679 --> 00:10:43.729
And we have been called to the kingdom for such a time as this.

00:10:43.730 --> 00:11:04.911
And it's time for you, behind this camera right now, to get a backbone like a crowbar and expect the unexpected—to be expecting God to do something huge through you. It just takes one spark to light a whole forest fire.

00:11:04.912 --> 00:11:16.388
And he said, 'Pray for the revival.'And then he said, 'Pray for Elon Musk.'There's enough here even right now that we can pray that Elon Musk would have a visitation.

00:11:16.389 --> 00:11:21.209
I saw to pray for Elon Musk again. He said, 'I'm calling him in.

00:11:21.210 --> 00:11:26.529
I'm calling him.'Well, 'He's too dark. I don't know. He'll never.'No.

00:11:26.530 --> 00:11:38.003
The Lord said as I was being persecuted on Facebook, they told me they'd call me, and then they told me they'd call me again, and they keep giving me the runaround.

00:11:38.004 --> 00:11:44.541
And that's when I said, 'Lord, why is it the body of Christ doesn't have a faith book?

00:11:44.542 --> 00:11:51.256
Why is it that the body of Christ is always having to use what's the trend?

00:11:51.257 --> 00:12:00.181
Why are we not the trendsetters? Why is Facebook the leader? Why is Instagram the leader? Why is TikTok the leader?

00:12:00.182 --> 00:12:09.833
Why is the body of Christ not the head?'And he talked about the money, because the body of Christ chokes on money. You go, 'Well, we can't have that.

00:12:09.834 --> 00:12:23.759
You know, the love of money is the root of all evil.'But that's why I said you're ignorant: because the Lord wants you to have the exceedingly abundantly above all that you ask or think to be able to have platforms to bring forth the glory.

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:29.677
Then whenever we're able to say what we want to say and talk about Jesus where they don't say, 'You know what?

00:12:29.678 --> 00:12:35.298
We're censoring you.'They turn me off like they did. 'We don't like that you're talking about Jesus.

00:12:35.299 --> 00:12:45.518
Don't come back,'and they won't give you an excuse other than, 'We don't want you on our platform anymore.'Even with 70,000 subscribers and followers, 'We don't care.

00:12:45.519 --> 00:12:52.660
There's the button.'Do you understand? And then the Lord showed me, 'Why is it the body of Christ can't have a Facebook?

00:12:52.661 --> 00:12:59.599
Why can't we believe for that?'Mark Zuckerberg had an idea, but why not us?

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:06.554
But it takes us to have a bigger mentality than always thinking of the one-eyed monster with the TV.

00:13:06.555 --> 00:13:12.078
And now the church is chasing TV. And I hate to say it, but TV's out.

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:16.406
It's not the cool thing anymore. I mean, who watches Christian television very much?

00:13:16.407 --> 00:13:20.697
Not us. I don't know very many of the younger generation that does.

00:13:20.698 --> 00:13:27.933
Maybe a handful of them, but a lot of boomers maybe, but a lot of the younger generation—Braden, he goes, 'TV?

00:13:27.934 --> 00:13:31.697
What?'They don't even know about TV. His generation doesn't even care about TV.

00:13:31.697 --> 00:13:36.078
So, you're going to lose a generation for the cause. Do you understand?

00:13:36.079 --> 00:13:48.319
No offense to Daystar and TBN or whoever, God TV or whatever it is, or Victory Network, but I'm going to tell you, you're going to lose a whole generation.

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:58.159
The boomers already either know or they don't know. But where's Generation X or the new AI generation?

00:13:58.160 --> 00:14:07.032
We've got to start thinking faster and be more effective. And that's what I'm praying: be more effective in these last days.

00:14:07.033 --> 00:14:12.542
Are you going to miss a generation for Jesus? What is drawing them in?

00:14:12.543 --> 00:14:30.078
When I was praying for Ericka and her ministry with Charlie Kirk, Turning Point, for the singing and the concerts and praying for things, how do we get the young generation to be engaged in church?

00:14:30.079 --> 00:14:46.155
I don't want to lose this generation. That's why even with the youth building, we're building this new youth facility because of the visions about the kids and the youth and the things that they're believing for.

00:14:46.156 --> 00:14:51.562
It takes somebody thinking outside of the box to reach a generation for Christ.

00:14:51.563 --> 00:14:58.738
And if we always think, 'Well, it's what the older people do,'then you're in trouble if you don't start planning now.

00:14:58.739 --> 00:15:04.293
And that's why I got so frustrated because the body of Christ is always thinking way behind.

00:15:04.294 --> 00:15:09.439
Well, we're chasing the TV and I'm like, 'No, no, no. You're off.

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:15.370
This is off. I know it by the Spirit of God. You're off. This is not right. You've got to get on the right road.

00:15:15.371 --> 00:15:21.274
We've got to get on the right road.'And now you see, well, Facebook's kind of fading out, but what's the new thing?

00:15:21.274 --> 00:15:27.980
What's going to be the new thing to reach this new generation? Ai, but what will AI do?

00:15:27.981 --> 00:15:34.756
And the Lord said, 'If you pray, I will show you the secret things of that which is to come.

00:15:34.757 --> 00:15:47.197
What will be trending in two years, five years, I will let you be the leader of the trend.'But if you keep chasing the trend, it's just like chasing the news, praying over the news.

00:15:47.197 --> 00:15:52.371
Well, you know, I saw today that President Trump said the war is over and then Iran said this.

00:15:52.372 --> 00:15:57.337
'What did I tell you was coming?'No. What did the Holy Spirit tell you was coming?

00:15:57.338 --> 00:16:02.299
Not Brandon Biggs. I've got to get it. It's just bad vocabulary.

00:16:02.300 --> 00:16:07.777
What did the Holy Spirit say? 'Israel. Pay attention to Israel.

00:16:07.778 --> 00:16:14.774
Israel will strike.'I didn't see America. I said Israel will blow up all their oil wells in the days ahead.

00:16:14.775 --> 00:16:23.813
Israel will do this. And anti-Semitism will rise up all over the world. Do you remember this? I didn't say America will do it.

00:16:23.814 --> 00:16:43.049
I said Israel will act alone and anti-Semitism will be at an all-time high against the Jews in the days ahead, and it will be so bad that they won't even be able to go to restaurants or to grocery stores without there being rioting and picketing and throwing rocks at them and things like that.

00:16:43.050 --> 00:17:06.719
It will be of biblical proportions. I said a new Hitler type of anti-Semitism—remember what I told you—will spring forth in Europe like it was in the Holocaust and it will be so bad that the Jews will flee and come back to Israel.

00:17:06.720 --> 00:17:10.354
I warned you of this. I saw this. It was a very detailed vision.

00:17:10.355 --> 00:17:22.476
Well, all these things are happening. Show them that. What is that?

00:17:22.477 --> 00:17:35.302
Trump's ceasefire. Do you show them? This is what the Holy Spirit said. So, we keep praying. We keep praying.

00:17:35.303 --> 00:17:41.225
So, as I was praying, I saw the wells of revival springing forth all over this land.

00:17:41.226 --> 00:18:06.182
And the Lord said, 'This will be a place of refuge to come and get a drink, and I will bring fresh anointing through your platform to bring forth where people don't have it.'You say, 'Well, I live in the middle of the country and we don't have a church like you're talking about and I've got to drive over 100 miles to go to a church like that because there isn't anybody around here like that.

00:18:06.183 --> 00:18:31.451
We're all dried up.'The Lord said, 'Be an oasis on the internet for people to come and get a drink.'He said it last night and he said, 'I'm going to as of now increase the anointing of the refreshing that will come through this camera so that you can have hope to get through your day.'Not through Brandon Biggs, but I'm telling you by the Holy Ghost.

00:18:31.452 --> 00:18:43.130
And I said, 'Lord, I'll yield to whatever you have for me.'I'll say whatever you want me to say, but I want you to drink from the well that never shall run dry.

00:18:43.131 --> 00:18:49.839
Fill our cup, Lord. That's why I sang it last night: 'I lift it up, Lord.'And I could feel the refreshing.

00:18:49.840 --> 00:18:54.784
I pray you got refreshed. We had over 42 salvations last night off that—30-something.

00:18:54.785 --> 00:19:00.215
It was amazing, wasn't it? Yes. I don't want to quit because it's so many days in a row.

00:19:00.216 --> 00:19:06.977
42—is that right? I try to memorize it because I like to keep track of how many we get in a month.

00:19:06.978 --> 00:19:13.519
It's amazing how many people come in; Jesus gets them. Okay, so that was part of what we saw last night.

00:19:13.520 --> 00:19:18.859
If you didn't watch that, I know it was almost four hours worth of videos.

00:19:18.860 --> 00:19:41.560
It's a long one, but I wasn't even going to do a video tonight until the Lord said, 'Brandon, this is what's coming.'I was sitting in church and I went over into the realm, and I could hardly hear what she was teaching the congregation on regarding the glory because I wasn't really there.

00:19:41.561 --> 00:19:44.914
I was looking over at what the Lord had me praying for tonight.

00:19:44.915 --> 00:19:49.243
Let me tell you what he said about tonight. He said, 'Do you see this now?

00:19:49.244 --> 00:19:57.127
Do you see the thumbnail?'You see the background, right? Did you put the background down?

00:19:57.128 --> 00:20:07.091
You see my background? That's what we are praying over. I saw attacks on our oil refineries and our oil facilities all over America.

00:20:07.092 --> 00:20:35.279
I know it was symbolic, but I could see Muslim men who looked like ISIS sympathizers casing our oil facilities and gas plants—natural gas, propane, and so on.

00:20:35.280 --> 00:20:47.806
I saw railroad tankers that look like propane tanks going down the rail.

00:20:47.807 --> 00:20:58.894
They were targeting propane tanks on trains—flammable fuels on these tankers on railroads.

00:20:58.895 --> 00:21:09.754
The Lord showed me those, and as I was in the spirit, I could see them moving down the railroad tracks in an area with a lot of trees.

00:21:09.755 --> 00:21:17.058
This looked like an area probably in the East because we don't have trees that look like that until you get over into Arkansas.

00:21:17.059 --> 00:21:25.809
Oklahoma is pretty prairie in some parts with a lot of red dirt.

00:21:25.810 --> 00:21:36.051
As I was looking into this, I saw railroad cars and the targeting of our electric grid.

00:21:36.052 --> 00:21:46.578
The Lord said, 'Pray over this tonight. This is a major assignment and you're on high alert for this.'That's what I saw.

00:21:46.579 --> 00:21:54.132
It was very detailed visions as I was in church; it was very clear, and the Lord said, 'Pray over this.

00:21:54.133 --> 00:22:02.588
This is very serious.'That's why you see what you see behind me. The other part was praying over the Strait.

00:22:02.589 --> 00:22:14.597
I told you I have to stretch my legs out; I'm going to have to get a little footrest or something because when I sit here, I like to prop my feet up.

00:22:14.598 --> 00:22:28.779
I put it on my trash can; I made my own little step stool here. I don't like to sit Indian style for so long that my legs go to sleep.

00:22:28.780 --> 00:22:40.696
As we were praying into it last night and praying over the Strait, I wanted to tell you this: I support President Trump.

00:22:40.697 --> 00:22:48.879
I pray for him to have wisdom. I know he's doing the best he knows how to do.

00:22:48.880 --> 00:22:59.575
If you really realize what a mess it all is—they don't come out and tell you the sky is falling like Chicken Little because one little spark of anything...

00:22:59.576 --> 00:23:03.882
look how volatile the market is. The war is over, everything goes...

00:23:03.883 --> 00:23:18.158
then it looks like a ceasefire is over, then I think there's going to be a ceasefire again, and the economy fluctuates just by one word out of a man's mouth.

00:23:18.159 --> 00:23:27.954
I haven't seen anything like it. If you come out as a president and say this or that, all of a sudden you're powerful.

00:23:27.955 --> 00:23:35.753
You can't say the sky is falling because if the sky is falling, people are selling everything and bunkering down in a hole.

00:23:35.754 --> 00:23:47.910
I saw Mark Zuckerberg down in there looking at the hole, like, 'Oh God, what's going on?'and I kept seeing Mark Zuckerberg sticking his head out this peephole.

00:23:47.911 --> 00:23:58.843
I keep seeing it all the time. I was like, 'What is that guy doing?'The other part was, do you remember when I told you I saw a leader over France?

00:23:58.844 --> 00:24:09.935
I said this man will be homosexual and will be a forerunner to take over France in the days ahead.

00:24:09.936 --> 00:24:23.181
He will have the same kind of spirit that is over the guy at CNN; he will be very similar in the way he acts, like the gray-haired guy, Anderson Cooper.

00:24:23.182 --> 00:24:29.157
I said he's similar to Anderson Cooper in the way he carries himself and talks.

00:24:29.158 --> 00:24:38.345
I said I saw a man running for president who will be over France and will be homosexual.

00:24:38.346 --> 00:24:45.893
I didn't necessarily know who this man is, just that he's coming.

00:24:45.894 --> 00:25:03.519
Braden said he's been doing research and this man right here is openly gay and is friends with Emmanuel Macron, and Emmanuel Macron wants him to be the next leader of France.

00:25:03.520 --> 00:25:11.999
Now, he doesn't look like Anderson Cooper—his hair is not gray—but I never heard him speak to see if he carries himself like Anderson Cooper.

00:25:12.000 --> 00:25:18.864
Or was it a type and shadow just telling me he's gay? I don't know, I just think it's interesting.

00:25:18.865 --> 00:25:37.038
I guess they're good friends. Maybe a little gray hair there?

00:25:37.039 --> 00:25:48.197
A little bit. Interesting. We'll see where that goes. Maybe there'll be another one.

00:25:48.198 --> 00:25:53.678
2027, the Lord said. But why is the Lord telling us about this ahead of time?

00:25:53.679 --> 00:26:09.437
Because I saw a lot of persecution coming with your First Amendment rights in France and a major rising up of antisemitism.

00:26:09.438 --> 00:26:14.479
The Lord said this is what we're praying for—the revival and these things. I want to skip all that.

00:26:14.480 --> 00:26:19.307
Real quick, Braden has some things he wants to show you, and then we're just going to jump in the river.

00:26:19.308 --> 00:26:33.234
I don't want to take a lot of your time. FBI warns Iranian hackers may be targeting critical U.S.

00:26:33.235 --> 00:26:48.409
water and energy systems. What did the Holy Spirit tell you? Targeting.

00:26:48.410 --> 00:26:59.394
I said water facilities; I said you better pray over your water facilities and energy.

00:26:59.395 --> 00:27:15.702
